  "summary": "Jacob Misiorowski is a tall, right-handed pitcher with some of the most electric stuff in the minors, consistently hitting triple digits with his fastball and featuring two wipeout breaking balls. While he was a top prospect expected to debut in 2025, he made his MLB debut in June 2025, became an All-Star in 2025, and is projected to be an Opening Day starter for the Milwaukee Brewers in 2026. His command has been a work in progress, but his raw talent offers front-end starter or elite reliever upside.",
